                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7070" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0487</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10280 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国美“摸鱼门”：知识型员工的管理与激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gome&#39;s Cyberslacking Incident: Management and motivation of knowledge-based employees</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱国玮，陆金凤、黄静、郑静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国美控股集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国美；家电零售行业；知识型员工；战略性人力资源管理；数字化人力资源管理；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Gome; home appliance retail industry; knowledge-based employees; strategic human resource management; digital human resource management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">移动互联网的发展使得家电产品消费行为发生变化，线上渠道崛起，传统线下渠道受到冲击。作为曾经家电零售行业的龙头企业，国美的发展陷入瓶颈，原有的市场份额被不断侵蚀。为了生存与发展，国美开始新零售战略转型。一系列变革措施接踵而至，员工加班加点、通宵达旦成为常态。2021年11月16日，一份国美内部通报员工摸鱼的文件流出，显得与如火如荼的转型变革格格不入。网友针对国美利用数字化手段监控员工上班行为是否侵犯隐私、员工摸鱼是否合理、企业如何管理摸鱼员工等问题展开激烈讨论。“摸鱼门”事件也让国美陷入舆论风波，企业的发展受到市场质疑。随着战略的转变，企业的人力资源管理应该做出哪些调整？在转型的关键时期，员工为什么会摸鱼？企业又该如何管理摸鱼员工？本案例旨在引导学生理解传统企业互联网化转型背景下知识型员工的管理与激励问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The mobile internet development has led to changes in the consumer behavior of appliances, the rise of online channels, and the impact on traditional offline channels. As a leading home appliance retail industry enterprise, Gome&#39;s development is in a bottleneck, and its original market share is being eroded continuously. In order to survive and develop, Gome started the new retail strategy transition. On November 16, 2021, a document of Gome&#39;s internal notification of staff cyberslacking was released, which seemed out of place with the transition change in full swing. The netizens are heatedly discussing whether Gome&#39;s use of digital means to monitor employees&#39; behavior at work is an invasion of privacy, whether it is reasonable for employees to cyberslacking, and how the company manages to cyberslacking employees. The cyberslacking incident also put Gome into the public opinion storm, and the market questioned the development of the enterprise. With the change of strategy, what adjustments should be made to the enterprise&#39;s human resource management? In the critical period of transition, why do employees appear to cyberslacking phenomenon? And how should the enterprise manage the cyberslacking employees? This case aims to guide students in understanding the management and motivation of knowledge-based employees in the context of the Internet-based transition of traditional enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">职业倦怠；工作匹配理论；战略性人力资源管理；知识型员工；知识型员工的激励；数字化人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
